{"word":"G3538 - νίπτω - níptō - nip'-to - Wash","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">níptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">nip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wash</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கழுவு"},{"paragraph":"to wash"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>To <i>cleanse</i> (especially the hands or the feet or the face); ceremonially to <i>perform ablution</i>: - wash. Compare <a href=\"#/G3068 - λούω - loúō - loo'-o/3068\">G3068</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3537/3537\">G3537</a>, <a href=\"#/G3538/3538\">G3538</a>, <a href=\"#/G449/449\">G449</a>"}]}